         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">6/8/61. ¶ Dear Dr. Ellery ¶  ¶ The walk and lines of trees were kept so far south through the reserve as it could possibly be effected. If unsurmountable obstacles exist to locate the Observatory, as ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">61.08.06b</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Robert Ellery</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Melbourne Observatory Collection, Museum Victoria, Melbourne</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">6/8/61.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Dear Dr. Ellery</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The walk and lines of trees were kept so far south through the reserve as it could possibly be effected. If unsurmountable obstacles exist to locate the Observatory, as I lastly suggested, a little further northward, then people must contend themselfes to walk around such enclosure as you may put up around the observatory reserve.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See M to C. Hodgkinson, 20 August 1861, and notes thereto.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Yours very truly</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. Mueller</p>
         </div>
      </body>
